title: [Cleric Guild, Annex]
description: An expansive mural rendered in bas-relief upon the limestone wall depicts scenes from the Ur-Daemon war.  The intermittent bell chimes echo throughout the annex, hardly muffled by the plush rug spanning the floor.  Fragrant incense wafts in from the adjoining alcoves.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southwest
